videos.description: Baylor's Ishmail Wainright throws the full-court football pass to Rico Gathers who makes the catch, turns and hits the 3-pointer at the buzzer to put the Bears up over Kansas at the half.
videos.headline: Full-court pass results in Baylor buzzer-beater

videos.description: After Baylor's Rico Gathers hits his first ever 3-pointer for the Bears at the first half buzzer, he races off the court and chest bumps a Baylor trainer, sending him tumbling to the ground. Oops.
videos.headline: Trainer can't handle chest bump from Rico Gathers

videos.description: Frank Mason III credits his teammate's poise down the stretch in a 66-60 win over Baylor and discusses the team's drive to improve as the tournament approaches.
videos.headline: Mason on 'hard fought' win on road over Baylor
